raw_text:
Great choice! Data Science is an exciting field. And good news — the GRE is **not required** for the Data Science program.

Now, when would you like to start, and will you be attending full-time or part-time?

---actions---
```json
[
  {
    "type": "set_fields",
    "fields": [
      { "field_id": "program", "value": "data_science" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "ask_choice",
    "question": "When would you like to start?",
    "options": [
      { "label": "Fall 2026", "value": "fall_2026" },
      { "label": "Spring 2027", "value": "spring_2027" }
    ]
  }
]
```

Got it — Spring 2027! A couple more quick questions to wrap up this section: will you be attending full-time or part-time, and have you previously applied to Northfield?

---actions---
```json
[
  {
    "type": "set_fields",
    "fields": [
      { "field_id": "start_term", "value": "spring_2027" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "ask_choice",
    "question": "Will you be attending full-time or part-time?",
    "options": [
      { "label": "Full-time", "value": "full_time" },
      { "label": "Part-time", "value": "part_time" }
    ]
  }
]
```

Full-time it is! One last question for this section — have you previously applied to Northfield?

---actions---
```json
[
  {
    "type": "set_fields",
    "fields": [
      { "field_id": "enrollment_type", "value": "full_time" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "ask_choice",
    "question": "Have you previously applied to Northfield?",
    "options": [
      { "label": "No", "value": "no" },
      { "label": "Yes", "value": "yes" }
    ]
  }
]
```

Program section is all set! Here's what we have:

Now let's move on to your personal information. Could you start with your full legal name, date of birth, and citizenship country?

---actions---
```json
[
  {
    "type": "set_fields",
    "fields": [
      { "field_id": "prior_application", "value": false }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "show_preview",
    "title": "Program Selection — Complete",
    "sections": [
      {
        "title": "Program Selection",
        "fields": [
          { "label": "Program", "value": "Data Science (MS)" },
          { "label": "Start Term", "value": "Spring 2027" },
          { "label": "Enrollment", "value": "Full-time" },
          { "label": "Prior Application", "value": "No" }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
]
```

I can see this is your resume — lots of great experience! Let me confirm where to assign it.

---actions---
```json
[
  {
    "type": "ask_choice",
    "question": "This looks like your resume. Which document field should I assign it to?",
    "options": [
      { "label": "Resume / CV (Recommended)", "value": "resume" },
      { "label": "Additional Supporting Document", "value": "additional_docs" }
    ]
  }
]
```
